dataItem-j8l6dllw1.text: Mobile Grocery Expiration Management

dataItem-j8o2opwo.text: Know exactly when your food is going to expire, without lifting a finger.

dataItem-j8o2vu45.text:
• Receive notifications when your food is about to expire.

  • Check on the status of any food in your fridge or pantry.

  • Automatically know what you need to buy on your next trip.

  • Save money by never letting your food expire.

dataItem-j8o3e3ad.text: Shopping List

dataItem-j8o3e3am.text:
• Receive notifications when you're in store about the foods you need.

  • Get coupons for the products you're shopping for in app.

  • Browse the best deals in all the grocery stores in your area to get the best deals on precisely wha you buy.

dataItem-j8o3hkoc.text: Smart Recipes

dataItem-j8o3hkof.text:
• When you need them, get recipes on food that's abut to expire.

  • Get tips based on your preferences on how to cook meal with your current inventory.

  • Save money and eat better by making your own meals more often and preventing your food from expiring.
